---
/**
 * Homepage - Founder Journey Landing Page
 *
 * A narrative-driven page for media buyers discovering terminal workflows.
 * The story is the hero. Numbers do the work.
 *
 * Structure:
 * 1. Hero - proof-first headline that earns attention
 * 2. Origin - compressed journey from UI to terminal
 * 3. The Shift - what changed, in terms they feel
 * 4. The Build - what you're creating, the trade
 * 5. Invitation - clear, single ask
 */
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
import EmailSignup from '../components/EmailSignup.astro';
import LogoAnimated from '../components/LogoAnimated.astro';
import SocialLinks from '../components/SocialLinks.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Channel47 — Claude Code plugins for media buyers"
  description="Free, open-source Claude Code plugins for Google Ads. Audit accounts, build campaigns, and automate the grind. From someone who can't code."
>
  <main class="page">
    <!-- Atmospheric orb - subtle warmth behind content -->
    <div class="atmosphere" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="atmosphere__orb"></div>
    </div>

    <Prose width="default">
      <!-- Hero: Proof-first, earns attention -->
      <header class="hero">
        <p class="hero__overline" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="1">Claude Code Plugins for Media Buyers</p>
        <h1 class="hero__headline" data-animate="blur-in" data-stagger="2">
          I audited 8 Google Ads accounts in 10 minutes.
        </h1>
        <div class="hero__terminal" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="3">
          <span class="hero__prompt" aria-hidden="true">~</span>
          <span class="hero__command">From my terminal.</span>
          <span class="hero__cursor" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="hero__proof" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="4">
          25 campaigns. 30+ ads. RSA best practices, sitelinks, callouts, structured snippets.
          Claude found the gaps, suggested fixes, and made the changes itself.
        </p>
        <p class="hero__kicker" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="5">
          I don't know how to code.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- CTA: Early placement for those ready to act -->
      <div class="cta cta--early" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="6">
        <EmailSignup placeholder="your@email.com" tag="hero" />
        <p class="cta__hint">Free plugins. Just need Claude Pro (~$20/mo).</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider divider--spaced" data-animate="fade-in" data-stagger="6" />

      <!-- Origin: Their starting point → your current state -->
      <section class="story">
        <div class="story__block" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="5">
          <p>
            A year ago I was clicking through the Google Ads UI like everyone else.
            Slow. Tedious. Managing 25+ accounts meant living inside dashboards I hated.
          </p>
          <p>
            Then I started experimenting with Claude.
          </p>
          <p>
            Not as a chatbot. <span class="story__emphasis">As a coworker.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story__block" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="6">
          <p>
            First Claude 3.5 Haiku. Then Sonnet. Now I run Claude Opus 4.5 in my terminal every day.
            Somewhere along the way, "experimenting with AI" became "I produce 10,000 lines of code daily
            and I still couldn't write a for-loop from scratch."
          </p>
          <p>
            I built an MCP server. Claude built most of it, honestly. Now my media buying happens
            in the terminal. It's faster. It's more fun. I actually enjoy the work again.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" data-animate="fade-in" data-stagger="6" />

      <!-- The Build: What you're creating -->
      <section class="story">
        <div class="story__block" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="7">
          <p class="story__lead">
            I'm building an open source marketplace for Claude Code plugins.
            Specifically for media buyers like me.
          </p>
          <p>
            Everything is free. You just need a Claude Pro subscription (around $20/month).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story__block" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="8">
          <p>
            Why free? Two reasons.
          </p>
          <p>
            First, I want your feedback. These tools get better when people actually use them
            and tell me what's broken, what's missing, what would make their work easier.
          </p>
          <p>
            Second, I think open source is how this should work. Intelligence is becoming a commodity.
            The value is in knowing how to use it. <span class="story__emphasis">That's what I'm sharing.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" data-animate="fade-in" data-stagger="8" />

      <!-- Proof: The 10-minute audit story -->
      <section class="proof" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="9">
        <div class="proof__header">
          <p class="proof__overline">What 10 minutes looks like now</p>
          <div class="proof__stats">
            <div class="proof__stat">
              <span class="proof__stat-value">8</span>
              <span class="proof__stat-label">accounts</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proof__stat">
              <span class="proof__stat-value">25</span>
              <span class="proof__stat-label">campaigns</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proof__stat">
              <span class="proof__stat-value">30+</span>
              <span class="proof__stat-label">ads checked</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="proof__body">
          <p>
            RSA best practices. Sitelinks, callouts, structured snippets.
            Claude found the gaps, suggested specific fixes, then made the changes itself.
          </p>
          <p class="proof__closer">
            All from the terminal. While I had coffee.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="proof__coda">
          This is where media buying is going. I'm just getting there early.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" data-animate="fade-in" data-stagger="9" />

      <!-- The Belief -->
      <section class="story" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="10">
        <div class="story__block">
          <p>
            Right now, the focus is media buying. That's where I live every day.
          </p>
          <p>
            Later, maybe this expands. Design. Analytics. Creative. I'm not sure yet.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm not an expert on these tools. But I am a daily practitioner. Someone who optimizes
            systems because I can't help myself. Someone who'd rather spend an hour automating
            a task than do it manually twice.
          </p>
          <p class="story__emphasis">
            If that sounds like you, we should probably be in touch.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Final CTA: The invitation -->
      <section class="invitation" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="11">
        <div class="invitation__container">
          <h2 class="invitation__headline">Join the list.</h2>
          <p class="invitation__pitch">
            First access to plugins as I release them. Updates on what's working (and what isn't).
            No pitch decks. No courses to sell. Just tools and honest notes from someone figuring this out in public.
          </p>
          <div class="invitation__form">
            <EmailSignup placeholder="your@email.com" tag="manifesto" />
          </div>
          <p class="invitation__cadence">
            1–2 emails per month, when I have something worth sharing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer: Logo + Social as unified closing -->
      <footer class="page-footer" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="12">
        <div class="page-footer__logo">
          <LogoAnimated delay={200} />
        </div>
        <div class="page-footer__social">
          <SocialLinks />
        </div>
      </footer>
    </Prose>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* =========================================
   * PAGE LAYOUT
   * Full viewport, generous whitespace
   * ========================================= */
  .page {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding-block-start: max(var(--space-14), env(safe-area-inset-top, 0px) + var(--space-8));
    padding-block-end: max(var(--space-16), env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px) + var(--space-10));
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  @media (min-width: 480px) {
    .page {
      padding-block-start: var(--space-16);
      padding-block-end: var(--space-20);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .page {
      padding-block-start: var(--space-20);
      padding-block-end: var(--space-24);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .page {
      padding-block-start: var(--space-24);
    }
  }

  @media (min-height: 800px) {
    .page {
      padding-block-start: 10vh;
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * ATMOSPHERE
   * Subtle orb effect for depth
   * ========================================= */
  .atmosphere {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: -1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .atmosphere__orb {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    left: 20%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: min(900px, 130vw);
    height: min(700px, 90vh);
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse 100% 100% at 50% 40%,
      var(--color-accent-glow) 0%,
      oklch(20% 0.025 35 / 0.15) 40%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    filter: blur(120px);
    animation: orb-pulse 30s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }

  @keyframes orb-pulse {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.4;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.6;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.05);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * HERO
   * Proof-first headline with strong hierarchy
   * ========================================= */
  .hero {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .hero__overline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__overline {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    }
  }

  .hero__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    letter-spacing: var(--optical-display);
    line-height: var(--leading-none);
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
    max-width: 16ch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 480px) {
    .hero__headline {
      font-size: var(--fluid-5xl);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__headline {
      font-size: var(--fluid-6xl);
      letter-spacing: var(--optical-hero);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }
    .hero {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .hero__headline {
      font-size: var(--fluid-7xl);
    }
  }

  .hero__terminal {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fluid-base);
    background: var(--color-bg-deep);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8) 0;
  }

  .hero__prompt {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    user-select: none;
  }

  .hero__command {
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }

  .hero__cursor {
    width: 2px;
    height: 1.2em;
    background: var(--color-fg-muted);
    animation: cursor-blink 1s step-end infinite;
    margin-left: var(--space-1);
  }

  @keyframes cursor-blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__terminal {
      font-size: var(--fluid-lg);
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero__cursor {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .hero__proof {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--type-prose-size);
    line-height: var(--type-prose-leading);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0;
    max-width: var(--measure-prose);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__proof {
      font-size: var(--fluid-lg);
    }
  }

  .hero__kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--type-prose-size);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__kicker {
      font-size: var(--fluid-lg);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * CTA
   * Email signup placements
   * ========================================= */
  .cta--early {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .cta__hint {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 0 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cta--early {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-14);
    }
    .cta__hint {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * DIVIDER
   * Subtle section breaks
   * ========================================= */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent 0%,
      var(--color-border-subtle) 20%,
      var(--color-border-subtle) 80%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    border: none;
    margin-block: var(--space-10);
  }

  .divider--spaced {
    margin-block: var(--space-14);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .divider {
      margin-block: var(--space-14);
    }
    .divider--spaced {
      margin-block: var(--space-20);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * STORY
   * Narrative sections
   * ========================================= */
  .story {
    max-width: var(--measure-prose);
  }

  .story__block {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .story__block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .story__block p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--type-prose-size);
    line-height: var(--type-prose-leading);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--paragraph-spacing) 0;
  }

  .story__block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .story__block p {
      font-size: var(--fluid-lg);
    }
  }

  .story__lead {
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: var(--color-fg) !important;
  }

  .story__emphasis {
    color: var(--color-fg);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
  }

  /* =========================================
   * PROOF
   * The 10-minute audit highlight - metrics-forward
   * ========================================= */
  .proof {
    max-width: var(--measure-wide);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof {
      padding: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  .proof__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__header {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  .proof__overline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5) 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__overline {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }
  }

  .proof__stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__stats {
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  .proof__stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-1);
  }

  .proof__stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    line-height: var(--leading-none);
    letter-spacing: var(--optical-display);
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__stat-value {
      font-size: var(--fluid-5xl);
    }
  }

  .proof__stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__stat-label {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
  }

  .proof__body {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .proof__body p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--type-prose-size);
    line-height: var(--type-prose-leading);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
  }

  .proof__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__body p {
      font-size: var(--fluid-md);
    }
  }

  .proof__closer {
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: var(--color-fg) !important;
  }

  .proof__coda {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof__coda {
      font-size: var(--type-prose-size);
      padding-top: var(--space-6);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * INVITATION
   * Final CTA section - the crescendo
   * ========================================= */
  .invitation {
    margin-top: var(--space-16);
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .invitation__container {
    max-width: var(--measure-prose);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-bg-elevated) 0%,
      var(--color-bg-surface) 100%
    );
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .invitation {
      margin-top: var(--space-24);
      padding-top: var(--space-16);
    }
    .invitation__container {
      padding: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  .invitation__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    letter-spacing: var(--optical-display);
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .invitation__headline {
      font-size: var(--fluid-4xl);
    }
  }

  .invitation__pitch {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--type-prose-size);
    line-height: var(--type-prose-leading);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8) 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .invitation__pitch {
      font-size: var(--fluid-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  .invitation__form {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .invitation__cadence {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .invitation__cadence {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================
   * FOOTER
   * Logo + social closing
   * ========================================= */
  .page-footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-32);
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .page-footer {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .page-footer {
      margin-top: 12rem;
      padding-top: var(--space-14);
    }
  }

  .page-footer__logo {
    opacity: 0.7;
    transition: opacity var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .page-footer__logo:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .page-footer__social {
    opacity: 0.4;
    transition: opacity var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .page-footer__social:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* =========================================
   * REDUCED MOTION
   * ========================================= */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .atmosphere__orb {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }
  }
</style>
